body: Last night I had a dream that Dan and Phil put out a new video and at the end Dan was like, “no it’s not dramatic enough” and he went into this huge dance routine and did some video editing where there were multiple Dans on the screen dancing at once and then at the very end he came out as bisexual and honestly, if Dan ever did make a coming out video that is exactly how he would do it
